init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was tired of being called names and being told that he was not good enough for her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was diagnosed with Bipolar disorder and was put on medication.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was the one who was there for her when she needed him the most.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She told the friend that she will never let him go as he was the one who helped her get better.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The friend was happy to hear this and told her to go and tell him how she felt.
